description.en:
uGMC makes ownership of cute Ethereum history accessible to everyone.
Genesis MoonCats are the rarest and most valuable assets of MoonCat Rescue, a project founded in mid-2017 by ponderware.
MoonCat Rescue was rediscovered by a community of digital archaeologists in March 2021, and has grown to become a strong community of thousands of cat-owners who prize the cats for their rich collectability, aesthetic, and history.
